title: dbAccess Japan Corporate Day
body:
Hong Kong & Singapore: March 12-14 in Hong Kong & March 15 in Singapore
Deutsche Bank is pleased to invite you to our 4th Annual dbAccess Japan Corporate Day, which will be held at the Deutsche Bank Hong Kong Office, International Commerce Centre, on March 12-14 (Monday-Wednesday) and Deutsche Bank Singapore Office, One Raffles Quay, on March 15 (Thursday).
